description:
Vanilla (5.3oz) Skyr Icelandic-Style Strained Non-Fat Yogurt.
Skyr is the traditional yogurt of Iceland that has been made for over 1,000 years. Our yogurt is a thick, creamy, strained yogurt with a high protein count. True to Icelandic tradition, siggi’s products are made with simple ingredients and not a lot of sugar. Mainstream yogurts can have up to 25g of sugar per serving. Our skyr contains only 8-11g of sugar and 14 - 15g of protein per 5.3oz cup.
All Natural
Milk from grass-fed cows
No aspartame
No sucralose
No gelatin
No artificial colorings
No preservatives
No high fructose corn syrup
title: Siggi's® Nonfat Vanilla Icelandic Style Yogurt - 5.3oz
bullet_description: Milk Fat Level: does not contain milk fat
